Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.28,0:00:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无垠的时间停止心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.82,0:00:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人无声息地自燃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.96,0:00:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都没有发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界异常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被红世之火笼罩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 剩下15分钟 自由活动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.25,0:02:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别做危险的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.21,0:02:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩伴不在的话就没精打采啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 吵架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.71,0:02:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那佐藤真的是感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.71,0:02:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 绪竹同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很在意佐藤请假？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢吉田同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要向坂井同学表白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二是我的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向坂井同学表白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么模棱两可的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后伤心的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧 能说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有个机会...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.98,0:03:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的序章
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:03:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来“星黎殿”也空荡荡的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这“星黎殿”作为载体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了那秘宝中的秘宝“零时迷子”和这位赫卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗 赫卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如贝尔菲戈所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又自我封闭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道在哪里看来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为那样就能得出答案了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是这种天真无邪很可贵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的赫卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.18,0:04:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会伤害到赫卡特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.97,0:04:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 应该说是能让我们永生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在有个完全符合的样本在活动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是个有点令人担心的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.45,0:05:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我独自训练
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没被告知
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这是从来没有过的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是有很要紧的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说废话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.91,0:05:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真的一次也没做过？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔赫米纳说不需要进行这种训练
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔赫米纳是和阿拉斯托尔一起生活的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.22,0:05:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 一上手就做便当也许有点难度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要便当不可吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠叫你做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:05:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着悠二吃吉田一美的便当...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田一美？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就做一道基础菜——煎鸡蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别停
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.69,0:06:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先调整好呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答复一次就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 鹗祭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.95,0:06:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在明天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.83,0:06:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是个很盛大的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前经常和爸爸妈妈一起参加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很爱吃苹果糖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.97,0:07:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在夜市上出售的一种糖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天和夏娜一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜对祭典没什么兴趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,训练继续
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答复一次就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 不用怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是祭典的装饰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹗祭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么快就到这个季节了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 约坂井同学一起参加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候向他表白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶卡特琳娜 回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得赶快上学去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:08:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我中途走开了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明这是小夏娜初次下厨...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是千草的错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我训练不够
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别“训练”什么的说得这么郑重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,料理只要包含着爱意就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱意？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从哪个开始吃呢 想不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,料理慢慢学着做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 对了 明天有个祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小悠一起参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.90,0:08:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种闹哄哄的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早点回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮你穿单衣和服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告诉小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到小夏娜穿单衣和服的样子 肯定会眼前一亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二会...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得有股烧焦的味道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.24,0:09:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二 认真训练了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.76,0:09:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是夏娜你为什么没来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.91,0:09:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜 你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点东西要买
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.27,0:09:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再吃吉田同学的便当了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里气馁的话一辈子都无法开口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的鹗祭...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的祭典怎么过？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像会有飞艇 比往常的热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就男的跟男的去的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约一下女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:10:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池同学 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 前几天的事真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池同学为我说了很多话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会主动争取的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 吉田约我参加明天的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的事我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我而拒绝的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是不会原谅你的 也许
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.42,0:11:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 我自己也不知道是不是真的喜欢上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.07,0:11:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想清楚后 我也将参与竞争
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:11:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是 人多一点也许会更好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也加入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.97,0:12:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快乐鹗祭游
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 干嘛当真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开个玩笑 玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然至今都对祭典之类的毫无兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到小夏娜穿单衣和服的样子 肯定会眼前一亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这或许会很快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 感觉如何 老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被服务生赶出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用睡在那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡在这里好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无必要地有了个住处的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会留恋不舍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要离开的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:12:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.79,0:13:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何况你这里的女仆打扫得太勤快了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸妈就喜欢让家里干干净净的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们也就可以吃闲饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 我也省心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.71,0:13:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是想有人关心你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在期待什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧得更高了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么精神的话应该没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先睡一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.85,0:14:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约好坂井同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天一定能说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉气息很明显
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 只是因为这位小姑娘的周围隐藏着恒定的物体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 看起来是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:14:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 忘记自我介绍了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是“圣装驱逐者”卡穆欣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是“坚毅的山峰”贝希摩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想请你协助我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.17,0:15:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我觉得你是最佳人选
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.01,0:15:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是纠正这个城市的扭曲而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 请不要逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个看过后就会明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界的真实情况
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界的...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马可西亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才没有挑衅的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是查看情况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 和大姐一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果玛乔里小姐她们要离开的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此要特训了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火炬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者的代替物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为被怪物吞食了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:16:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他们...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.95,0:17:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他们...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的家人没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是成为助手的条件之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 妈妈 健都没事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.42,0:17:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是操控存在之力的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:17:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 明天是周六 本来是下午训练的...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也晚上训练好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.34,0:18:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了可以就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.37,0:18:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 那在祭典过后来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二 集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传给我的存在之力的量自己把握
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次瞬间集聚 像爆炸一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.59,0:18:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但留下微乎其微的量维持存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.47,0:18:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的只是加大了传输量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须形成瞬间爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.48,0:19:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二的存在之力虽然不大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在瞬间集聚的话会更能派上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不怎么会调节
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你让我留下维持自己存在的量...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.95,0:19:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你体内的“零时迷子”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.53,0:19:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在午夜零时会让你的存在之力完全恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心大胆地用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.49,0:19:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每晚 每晚 毫不厌倦地训练啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.72,0:19:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 打扰了你们卿卿我我的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.93,0:19:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么 关于新的迹象？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 来了个厉害角色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好也不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.11,0:19:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事一点也没告诉...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没感觉到战斗的迹象所以没说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 或许只是碰巧路过而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说这里有个了不得的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得稍微警惕一些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙发现它时的那个高兴劲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.57,0:20:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许你已经听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休多那又回到“化装舞会”了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 化装...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化装舞会 徒的团体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统率它的是被称为“三柱臣”的三人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫卡特 贝尔菲戈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及中途退出过的休多那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那些家伙采取行动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.57,0:20:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有点棘手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该考虑今后的打算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗 坂井悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.42,0:20:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？今后的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是离开这个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为得到悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“化装舞会”很有可能会潜入这个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.81,0:21:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我留在这里的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 很抱歉突然告诉你这个世界的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要让你协助我就必须让你知道一些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.66,0:21:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你察觉到世界的不谐调
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.08,0:21:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如刚才所见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个城市的火炬很多 扭曲得很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.89,0:21:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调整这种扭曲正是我们的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以才被称为“调律师”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.38,0:21:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要调律就必须得到土生土长的当地人的协助...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.94,0:21:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会立即动身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.18,0:21:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贸然行动很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:21:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开这个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.94,0:22:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和夏娜一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备工作正顺利进行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.65,0:22:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音 是那个家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.36,0:22:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化装舞会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星黎殿的活动异常
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.46,0:22:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零时迷子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解决完这里的事后赶过去
